<p id="p2">Last week, I was in LA for <a href="https://www.airbnb.com/release" rel="noopener noreferrer">Airbnb&rsquo;s 2025 Summer Release</a>. As part of the day&rsquo;s events, Federico and I interviewed Jud Coplan, Airbnb&rsquo;s Vice President of Product Marketing, and Teo Connor, Airbnb&rsquo;s Vice President of Design, for <a href="https://appstories.net/episodes/436" rel="noopener noreferrer">AppStories</a> to talk about <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/airbnb/id401626263" rel="noopener noreferrer">the new features and app</a> the company launched. It was a great conversation that you can watch on YouTube:</p>
